# Privacy Policy

Last updated: February 26, 2025

## Introduction
ZhiQu ("we", "us", or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.

## Information Collection
ZhiQu does not collect any personally identifiable information. All data (including quotes and notes you save) is stored locally on your device and is never uploaded to any server.

## Data Storage
• All quotes and notes are stored only on your local device
• App settings (theme, language preferences) are stored in UserDefaults
• We do not access, store, or share any of your personal data

## In-App Purchases
We offer in-app tips through Apple's StoreKit. All payment transactions are handled by Apple, and we cannot access your payment information.

## Third-Party Services
This app does not use any third-party analytics tools or advertising services.

## Children's Privacy
This app does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.

## Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:
[Your email address]
